<p>
The world beginnings to blur. The sand below begins to stick the bottom of your feet.
</p>
<btn>1. Continue walking.</btn>
#(if intelligence > 12 option 2 is visible)
<btn>2. Investigate.</btn>


while( <btn> != 2. Investigate )
    <p>
    You continue walking. Your feet are growing heavy.
    </p>
    <btn>1. Continue walking..</btn>
    #(if intelligence > 12 option 2 is visible)
    <btn>2. Investigate.</btn>

# once the user clicks 2. investigate 
<p>You get down on one knee for a closer look at the sand. It smells sugary.</p>

while( <btn> != 2. Investigate )
    <p>
    You continue walking. Your feet are growing heavy.
    </p>
    <btn>1. Continue walking.</btn>
    #(if intelligence > 12 option 2 is visible)
    <btn>2. Investigate closer.</btn>

# once the user clicks 2. investigate 
<p>You lean in closer to smell the sand. Definitely sugar.</p>
<btn>Continue walking.</btn>
<btn>2. Lick the sand.</btn>

